c: 20
v: 71
t: "He (Pharaoh) said, \"You believe in him before I give you permission? He (Moses) is certainly a great (expert) among you all who has taught you the magic. So I will definitely cut off your hands and your feet from opposite sides and I will definitely crucify you on the trunks of the palm trees, and you will definitely know which of us has more severe and more lasting punishment"